        <hl1>CANADIAN PACIFIC RESULTS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Timothy Pritchard</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Pritchard, Timothy</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Canadian Pacific Ltd doubled its second-quarter profit to 379 million Canadian dollars ($258 million), far above expectations, on 8 percent increase in revenue to 2.96 billion Canadian dollars (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Canadian transportation and natural resource conglomerate Canadian Pacific Ltd. doubled its second-quarter profit to 379 million Canadian dollars ($258 million), far above expectations, on an 8 percent increase in revenue to 2.96 billion Canadian dollars. Four of the Calgary company's five operating divisions had record returns.</p>
        <p>Timothy Pritchard</p>
      </block>
